#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:213 data/civ2civ3/buildings.ruleset:294
#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:218 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:223
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:244 data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:292
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With a Barracks III, each new land unit built in a city will automatically "
"have Veteran status, which means that its attack and defense strengths are "
"increased by 50%."
msgstr ""
"Med brakker blir alle nye landenheter veteraner. Det betyr at deres angreps "
"og forsvars styrke øker med 50%. Skadede land enheter som blir i byen for en "
