"Underholder innbyggerne i byen, gjør 3 ulykkelige borgere fornøyd. (Fire "
"etter oppdagelsen av elektrisitet.)"

#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:347 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reduces the corruption in a city by 50%, and makes the revolt cost of the "
"city 4 times bigger. (These effects are redundant in your capital city.)"
