#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:899 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:958
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:876
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increases the effect of a Factory and Mfg. Plant on the shield production of "
