"With both a Bank and a Marketplace in a city, the total bonus is 80%."
msgstr "Øker byens luksus- og skatte-bidrag med 50%."

#: data/royale/buildings.ruleset:225
#, fuzzy
msgid "Mercantile Exchange"
msgstr "Standard regelsett"

#: data/royale/buildings.ruleset:243
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increases the luxury good and tax output in a city by an additional 30%. "
"With a Mercantile Exchange, a Bank and a Marketplace in a city, the total "
"bonus is 110%."
msgstr "Øker byens luksus- og skatte-bidrag med 50%."

#: data/royale/buildings.ruleset:269
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With a Barracks, each new land unit built in a city (except siege units like "
"Catapults) will automatically have Veteran status, which means that its "
"attack and defense strengths are increased by 50%."
msgstr ""
"Med brakker blir alle nye landenheter veteraner. Det betyr at deres angreps "
"og forsvars styrke øker med 50%. Skadede land enheter som blir i byen for en "
"hel runde uten å forflytte seg blir helt reparert."

#: data/royale/buildings.ruleset:298
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With a Barracks II, each new land unit built in a city (except siege units "
"like Cannon and Artillery) will automatically have Veteran status, which "
"means that its attack and defense strengths are increased by 50%."
msgstr ""
"Med brakker blir alle nye landenheter veteraner. Det betyr at deres angreps "
"og forsvars styrke øker med 50%. Skadede land enheter som blir i byen for en "
"hel runde uten å forflytte seg blir helt reparert."

#: data/royale/buildings.ruleset:326
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With a Barracks III, each new land unit built in a city (except siege units "
"like Artillery and Howitzer) will automatically have Veteran status, which "
"means that its attack and defense strengths are increased by 50%."
msgstr ""
"Med brakker blir alle nye landenheter veteraner. Det betyr at deres angreps "
